## Audit Checklist

### Story 3.1: Display Train Positions on Map
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/map');
await page.waitForSelector('.leaflet-marker-icon');
await page.screenshot({ path: 'evidence-3-1-map.png' });
```
- [ ] Map renders centered on Portugal
- [ ] Train markers visible
- [ ] No console errors
- [ ] Renders in < 2 seconds

### Story 3.2: Color-Code Markers by Status
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/map');
const markers = page.locator('.train-marker');
// Check for green, blue, red markers
```
- [ ] Green markers present (available)
- [ ] Blue markers present (in-service)
- [ ] Red markers present (maintenance)
- [ ] Legend visible with color meanings
- [ ] Filter toggles work

### Story 3.3: Show Depot Locations
```typescript
// Playwright test:
await page.goto('/map');
await expect(page.locator('.depot-marker')).toBeVisible();
```
- [ ] Depot markers visible (different icon from trains)
- [ ] Depot capacity shown on hover
- [ ] Can toggle depots on/off

